      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ANOTHER ARTIST (1) had to overcome a check in the run but could manage only a distant third (16.55) in a Maiden over 272m at this track. Has the ability and looks hard to top. KILCOY PEARL (6) made it two minor placings on the trot when beaten second (18.56) in a Maiden at Richmond last time out. Expected to bounce back to best. POPPY'S FOX (4) has his first outing without a trial but profiles nicely for this. Likely to run well. VINNIE ZACAPA (5) is a Mischelle Edmunds-trained newcomer by Feral Franky out of Ephemeral. No favours with the draw and will need to begin well. Can sneak into the frame at his first appearance.",
